Sort of a 'defend the fort' type of map, CTs must stop the terriosts from planting the bomb at their base! Also there are many secrets! If you can't find them! PM me! or go in spec and look for them! 

Hope you give feedback, because I'm going to post a numerous amount of maps! Please contact me if you're going to add to a server! My name is Mr Muffinz(on steam) Enjoy!


To download this map, palce into your 'maps' folder in 'cstrike' if you don't know how, google or use youtube to find out! How I found out!
